Google Image Search Downloader
==============================

* A Proof-of-concept Chrome extension to save the full-size images returned by a Google image search query *

Installation
------------

* Download the unpacked extension
* Open browser page: chrome://flags
* enable "Experimental Extension APIs" and restart browser
* Open browser page: chrome://chrome/extensions/
* Enable developer mode

* Click on "Load unpacked extension" and select the extension folder

Usage
-----

* Go to google, search for images
* A Page Action icon will apear in the address bar
* Customize the search (query, size, type, etc)
* Click on the icon to download all photos. The photos will be downloaded at full-size and saved in your Downloads folder



